  "body": "Use a more intuitive name to choose between the default eth2 spec type. Also, align the API to other major Eth2.0 clients\r\n\r\n- [x] Remove `chain.name` option from `BeaconChain` since it's not used: https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/9fceb034282609f11efb0ce8acb74a0cb2107e25/packages/lodestar/src/chain/chain.ts#L80\r\n- [ ] Rename the library API and the CLI API to be on par and both use a `spec` name option\r\n- [ ] Consider deprecating `IChainOptions` entirely since none of its options seem to be used. https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/9fceb034282609f11efb0ce8acb74a0cb2107e25/packages/lodestar/src/chain/options.ts#L1-L4",
